---
name: budget_alert
temperature: 0.3
response_format: json
---

Write a friendly budget alert notification in Bahasa Indonesia.

## Budget status
Category: {{budget.category_name}}
Limit: {{budget.limit_amount | currency}}
Spent: {{budget.spent_amount | currency}}
Threshold reached: {{threshold_pct}}%
Days remaining in period: {{budget.days_remaining}}

## Response (JSON only)
{
  "push_title": "<max 50 chars>",
  "push_body": "<max 100 chars, friendly tone>",
  "full_message": "<2-3 sentences with context and suggestion>"
}
